{"tid":1933452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［風向］•  世界排華風氣升級，香港人要主動出擊分割","createTime":"2020-03-19T09:47:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T10:15:04.000Z","uid":287214,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bcb4ae96edd905de1ebda8046ee650e6f5086074","tid":1933452,"uid":287214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:47:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家都見到侵侵帶頭撥亂反正，要全世界知道肺炎係源自支那。剛剛見到巴西總統兒子亦都有開聲指責中國，應該為世界這悲劇附上責任。其實我個國家今次比支那國累到雞毛鴨血，又死人又冇得搞奧運又輸錢，呢獲野全世界一定要同佢地埋單。新一輪國際級排華將會旋風式到來。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人要醒目先發制人，要向全世界各大小平台輿論用1000陪嘅力站在國際呢一邊，令全世界再一次知道香港同支那嘅分別！ </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">抗疫期間大家冇得上街，要用國際思維加把勁，大家醒水！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f9c72850cce8e56fae6de9db42d63a5ed369dea7","tid":1933452,"uid":287214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:50:33.000Z","msg":"自己推唔郁"},{"pid":"0762116f31d4ceb885f5c66230687451af80d6f1","tid":1933452,"uid":89963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:52:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ffbb4dd4d28c18ed0f975fa2ef97f7099ba8d158","tid":1933452,"uid":209355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:53:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cfdaee39a09b407b3ed75e0732de572149994d98","tid":1933452,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:54:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5f51433e9d0134e2425046898fead2a6430df79","tid":1933452,"uid":287214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:56:00.000Z","msg":"大家請幫幫忙推推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img